SAFA has confirmed that Tendai Ndoro has been found guilty and received a two match suspension. His club Ajax Cape Town were also found guilty of fielding Ndoro and will forfeit matches against Platinum Stars, Polokwane City & Supersport United. They lose all three matches 3-0 & fined R50 000 on each offence. In this case Ajax are relegated and Platinum Stars will play in the relegation / promotion play-Offs.